et: Italian {it}cannellini{/it}, plural of {it}cannellino{/it} kind of hard candy, variety of white bean resembling the candy, probably from {it}cannella{/it} cinnamon, literally, small tube, from Medieval Latin {it}canella{/it}, diminutive of Latin {it}canna{/it}
